metadata.name: I Am Living #13
metadata.description:
A War Mask in abstract. Each mask is my vision of a future symbolic representation of strength and determination worn by a different person from day to day struggling with mental health. A running feature in this collection is the use of metallic paints. All works are hand painted and limited to 1 of 1. 
There will never be another. 
Each piece is signed by myself. 
Enjoy living.
